{"tid":1623064,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我見到子彈，好concern，麻煩大家幫手報警","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:23:54.000Z","uid":260256,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"070840a6e6c2363ac5a9d229ccb56b209e069527","tid":1623064,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:13:25.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位連登仔女幫手報警<br />\n<br />\n我喺長洲見到一粒疑似子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知extactly喺邊度，唔知呀，好似係東提嗰度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗰下好驚，一腳踢走咗，冇留意有冇飛咗落渠&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班警察叔叔係咪仲未搵返彈夾？會唔會比人射出嚟架？好擔心呀，希望佢哋快啲派人去搵啦，成個area都唔見人，實彈可以打死人架嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做個良好巿民，幫手報警，警察好幸苦架，邊個知元朗個彈夾拆開啲子彈去哂邊度就幫下啲警察叔叔啦，佢哋好辛苦架&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c4e166bd704bc6f687b7b25961c6a7df05701e","tid":1623064,"uid":171314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0abd6e7c70d709ad550557ef519cca462095012f","tid":1623064,"uid":260256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0c4e166bd704bc6f687b7b25961c6a7df05701e","tid":1623064,"uid":171314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"幫我推多兩下/spread出去<br />\np牌推唔郁，真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c814162847586110cdf1a5c4df077c80f667aa","tid":1623064,"uid":154783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:03:21.