.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好執走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要通報有關機構呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"提電話報警係會即時係電腦睇到你位置去判斷有冇報假案 好似係"},{"pid":"73be10125c9562f2afe6aa4cb656ac643ab2aa47","tid":1623064,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"講多小小<br />\n你有時報狗講街名, 點解電話狗會即刻知道<br />\n一來打字搵 二來你電話個位置係會即刻顯示係電腦<br />\n用 Skype 呢類 IP phone 報狗間唔中會以為電話撚狗, 會即刻問你點解電腦位置唔同"},{"pid":"fb55a4d070e8101e14a19ca90622b2ef76c0bd2c","tid":1623064,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73be10125c9562f2afe6aa4cb656ac643ab2aa47","tid":1623064,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"講多小小<br />\n你有時報狗講街名, 點解電話狗會即刻知道<br />\n一來打字搵 二來你電話個位置係會即刻顯示係電腦<br />\n用 Skype 呢類 IP phone 報狗間唔中會以為電話撚狗, 會即刻問你點解電腦位置唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁行開咗之後先醒起嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988f787e05ccbb0aa4ccb8e39bd285eaa8044140","tid":1623064,"uid":84741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"如果跌咗落坑渠佢哋有排撈"},{"pid":"3bad91778d41b697d8974ae492711a16ba942abf","tid":1623064,"uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1282941e08e5739a61943c7a4505bc121f31205","tid":1623064,"uid":89